collectors.titleDetails: (10 total Queries, 10 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: select DISTINCT title,c1t.code,c1t.mtID,c1.remarks,c1.status, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_c1 WHERE tbl_client_c1.mtID = c1.mtID and tbl_client_c1.wpID = 2 and tbl_client_c1.cID = 9) as x , (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_c1 WHERE tbl_client_c1.mtID = c1.mtID and tbl_client_c1.wpID = 2 and tbl_client_c1.cID = 9 and `updated_on` IS NOT NULL) as y from tbl_c1_titles as c1t, tbl_client_c1 as c1 where c1t.mtID = c1.mtID and c1.cID = 9 and c1.wpID = 2 order by mtID asc

select DISTINCT title,c1t.code,c1t.mtID,c1.remarks,c1.status, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_c2 WHERE tbl_client_c2.mtID = c1.mtID and tbl_client_c2.wpID = 2 and tbl_client_c2.cID = 9) as x , (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_c2 WHERE tbl_client_c2.mtID = c1.mtID and tbl_client_c2.wpID = 2 and tbl_client_c2.cID = 9 and `updated_on` IS NOT NULL) as y from tbl_c2_titles as c1t, tbl_client_c2 as c1 where c1t.mtID = c1.mtID and c1.cID = 9 and c1.wpID = 2 order by mtID asc

select DISTINCT title,c1t.code,c1t.mtID,c1.remarks,c1.status, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_c3 WHERE tbl_client_c3.mtID = c1.mtID and tbl_client_c3.wpID = 2 and tbl_client_c3.cID = 9) as x , (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_c3 WHERE tbl_client_c3.mtID = c1.mtID and tbl_client_c3.wpID = 2 and tbl_client_c3.cID = 9 and `updated_on` IS NOT NULL) as y from tbl_c3_titles as c1t, tbl_client_c3 as c1 where c1t.mtID = c1.mtID and c1.cID = 9 and c1.wpID = 2 order by mtID asc

select * , (select 100 - round(((SUM(ytd) - SUM(supp_bal)) / SUM(ytd)) * 100) from tbl_client_trial_balance as tb where tb.cID = 9 and tb.wpID = 2 and cfi.index = tb.index) as prog from tbl_client_file_index as cfi, tbl_file_index as fi where cfi.index = fi.fiID and cfi.wpID = 2 and cfi.cID = 9
select DISTINCT cfi.added_on,cfi.added_by,tu.name from tbl_users as tu, tbl_client_trial_balance as cfi where tu.userID = cfi.added_by and cfi.wpID = 2 and cfi.cID = 9

select *
        from tbl_client_trial_balance as cfi, tbl_file_index as fi
        where cfi.index = fi.fiID
        and cfi.wpID = 2
        and cfi.cID = 9

select * 
        from tbl_file_index as fi
        where fi.fiID >= 2
        and fi.fiID <= 7
